trans-unit.source: Enables clients to provide custom services to components on which the contract is implemented.
trans-unit.target: Lar klienter angi egendefinerte komponenter kontrakten implementeres-tjenester.

trans-unit.source: A component implements IProfferServiceContract to enable clients to offer services to the component.
trans-unit.target: En komponent som implementerer IProfferServiceContract for å aktivere klienter tilbyr tjenester til komponenten.

trans-unit.source: After a service has been offered to a component, other clients of the component can access the service.
trans-unit.target: Når en komponent fikk en tjeneste, kan andre komponenten-klienter tilgang til tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: Components typically implement IProfferServiceContract on the same type on which they implement <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract>.
trans-unit.target: Komponenter implementere vanligvis IProfferServiceContract på samme type som implementerer de <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract>.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract>

trans-unit.source: Clients use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IProfferServiceContract.ProfferService%2A> method to add an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract> to the set of service providers offered by a component.
trans-unit.target: Klienter som bruker den <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IProfferServiceContract.ProfferService%2A>metode for å legge til en <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract>settet med tjenesteleverandører som tilbys av en komponent.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IProfferServiceContract.ProfferService%2A>

trans-unit.source: Clients use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IProfferServiceContract.RevokeService%2A> method to remove an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract> from the set of service providers offered by a component.
trans-unit.target: Klienter som bruker den <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IProfferServiceContract.RevokeService%2A>metode for å fjerne en <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract>fra settet med tjenesteleverandører som tilbys av en komponent.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IProfferServiceContract.RevokeService%2A>

trans-unit.source: Adds a service to the set of services that can be accessed by clients of a component.
trans-unit.target: Legger til en tjeneste sett med tjenester som kan åpnes av klienter for en komponent.

trans-unit.source: The format of the `serviceIdentifier` parameter is defined by the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IProfferServiceContract> implementation.
trans-unit.target: Formatet for den `serviceIdentifier` parameter er definert av den <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IProfferServiceContract>implementeringen.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IProfferServiceContract>

trans-unit.source: A uniform resource identifier (URI) is the recommended identifier.
trans-unit.target: En uniform resource identifier (URI) er den anbefalte identifikatoren.

trans-unit.source: A string that identifies the service being offered.
trans-unit.target: En streng som identifiserer tjenesten tilbudt.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.IServiceProviderContract"></xref> that implements the service being offered.
Removes a service from the set of services offered by a component.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner en tjeneste fra settet med tjenester som tilbys av en komponent.

trans-unit.source: The format of the `serviceIdentifier` parameter is defined by the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IProfferServiceContract> implementation.
trans-unit.target: Formatet for den `serviceIdentifier` parameter er definert av den <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IProfferServiceContract>implementeringen.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IProfferServiceContract>

trans-unit.source: A uniform resource identifier (URI) is the recommended identifier.
trans-unit.target: En uniform resource identifier (URI) er den anbefalte identifikatoren.

trans-unit.source: A string that identifies the service being revoked.
trans-unit.target: En streng som identifiserer tjenesten blir tilbakekalt.
